Working with texts, charts, presentations, Internet, e-mail.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To provide knowledge on the opportunities of a personal computer, main software, and modern information technology; to provide skills necessary for work with text processing, spreadsheet, and presentation programmes; to introduce principles related to the internet, e-mail, and network etiquette, i.e. netiquette.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  - can work with text processing programmes; - can create text documents with complex structure, including divisions, tables and spreadsheet calculations, graphic objects, links, markers, and a table of contents; - can find information from the internet by using language appropriate for the search systems; - can do simple spreadsheet calculations and prepare diagrams; - can prepare presentations; - understands and can apply netiquette principles.
